          .coach-description
            Erin has been an assistant track and field and cross country coach at both University of Arizona and Northern Arizona University.  At NAU, Erin helped guide the men’s and women’s cross country teams to fourth and seventh place finishes respectively at Nationals. During her coaching career she has helped guide the training of three individual national champions, and dozens of All-Americans and conference champions. Erin is a graduate of the University of Texas, where she competed on squads capturing NCAA Regional and Big 12 Conference titles.
         
