      %h3 Katherine Phillips
      = image_tag "http://a2.sphotos.ak.fbcdn.net/hphotos-ak-ash4/313803_2459605335029_1399035378_32889434_1555514441_n.jpg", { :class => "coach-picture" }
      .coach-description
        Katherine is co-owner of Pike Athletics.  She is an NSCA Certified Strength and Conditioning Specialist (CSCS) and a Certified Coach by USA Track and Field, USA Cycling, and USA Triathlon.  She also works as a consultant to USA Paralympic Cycling.  Previously she was the assistant track and field and cross country coach at Johns Hopkins University.  A former USA Triathlon Junior National team member, Katherine is one of the first USA Triathlon Youth/Junior Certified Coaches.  She is a graduate of California State University San Marcos where she trained under the guidance of three time Olympian and former American record holder in the mile Steve Scott.
 